{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc6feecf90","title":"关于同意印度临时代表到北京谈判建立外交使团的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c29c468f95","index":0,"year":1950,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"fc6feecf90"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"42e9e9b47e","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李克农，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长。14]周，指周恩来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0ffb7b81c6","type":"title","text":"关于同意印度临时代表到北京谈判建立外交使团的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"42e9e9b47e","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"04ce5c1a86","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）本十九日各电均悉。同意你的意见，先给尼赫鲁去电，大意谓同意雁词森先生为临时代表，到北京谈判建立外交使团的初步与程序事宜。对英国答复则应当拖一下。外交部的同志们不了解拖一下的作用，认为“陷于借局”，这是不对的，这里并没有什么借局，主动权完全握在我们手中。拖一下的时间请你和李克农商定之。（二）同意为西藏问题所拟发之声明。（三）空运团事待与周“商后答复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"3b0b50e3b7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"4a14b593b4","type":"paragraph","text":"一月二十日上午一时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"7c3d525c02","type":"paragraph","text":"i尼赫鲁，当时任印度政府总理兼外交部部长。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"},{"id":"74330a78bd","type":"paragraph","text":"雁遇森，曾任印度驻国民党中国大便馆秘书。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90"}],"page":{"id":"8b0a19e405","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"fc6feecf90","start":184,"end":184}}}},"__N_SSG